{"tid":1913791,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【本土研究社】中資醫護設施工程播毒威水史","createTime":"2020-03-07T05:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T05:37:12.000Z","uid":138409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4336809de8fffc007cf9b1332b608f047e3c62fe","tid":1913791,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2893776630718391/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F2893776630718391%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=24dadef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2893776630718391/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9a1BLr0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9a1BLr0.jpg&h=5ded89b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【中資醫護設施工程播毒威水史】<br />\n<br />\n可能大家沒留意海外新聞，今次獲林鄭獎券基金直接批億元起竹篙灣及鯉魚門「隔離營」的<span style=\"color: gold;\">中交建系國企 (包括中國港灣及中國建築)</span>，其實近年不少醫護設施工程都「揚威海外」，例如近日就被澳洲政府發現<span style=\"color: gold;\">中交建子公司</span>John Holland於塔斯曼尼亞的新重建Royal Hobart Hospital<span style=\"color: gold;\">醫院大樓鉛水超標</span>，現時工程已無限期擱置，【註一】本地幾乎無任何消息及報導。<br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶，全中資擁有的John Holland，於2016年<span style=\"color: gold;\">承建澳洲柏斯兒童醫院時同樣有鉛水超標</span>。更嚴重是，還被澳洲工人揭發醫院內的<span style=\"color: gold;\">隔熱板含一級致癌物料石棉</span> (想知石棉有幾恐怖可參考 : <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3ayLqYZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ayLqYZ&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=b6685988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3ayLqYZ</a> ) ，引起公眾恐慌，整間醫院立即被隔離【註二】。<br />\n<br />\n其後澳國透過資訊自由(FOI)追查原因，發現John Holland引入了中交建長期合作的供應商<span style=\"color: gold;\">「中國遠大」</span>的建材物料出事，其後中國遠大事後解釋它們也並不知情，是其他背後中國供應商的問題【註三】，播毒事件亦無從問責。<br />\n<br />\n記得2015年同期，中國建築都有在香港牽起了啟德鉛水風波，其後政府試圖幫手將問題歸咎一名水喉匠使用含鉛焊料【註四】，所以一切只是水喉匠的錯，不關中資及背後中資建材供應鏈的事。<br />\n<br />\nJohn Holland作為中國一帶一路併購外地工程公司「走出去」的重要佈署，很清楚的顯示出中資國企如何透過承包海外工程項目，不知不覺間<span style=\"color: gold;\">混入中國本地來源不明的「過盛產能」</span>，令工程隱患更加隱藏及難以有效監察，那麼發現石棉及鉛就也不令人意外。 (順帶一提，<span style=\"color: gold;\">John Holland 也是沙中線工程醜聞的主角之一</span>，但我們沒有資訊自由法逼使港鐵交出工程黑幕。)<br />\n<br />\n如果中資承包建築物料供應鏈，根本接二連三不斷出事，還要興建的是關乎性命安危的設施，為何到我們要興建更高安全系數的檢疫設施，都可以如此輕率繞過立法會直接批錢給劣跡斑斑的中資負責?<br />\n<br />\n#唔可以鉛量<br />\n#隔離營<br />\n#想病毒死石棉毒死定鉛水毒死<br />\n#細路都唔放過<br />\n#中交建威水史系列<br />\n#一帶一路<br />\n#資訊自由法好重要<br />\n<br />\n【註一】Tasmanian Times : Lead-Contaminated Water at RHH<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2TtDN09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TtDN09&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=ac24d011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2TtDN09</a><br />\n<br />\n【註二】The West Australian : High lead levels found in drinking water at new children's hospital<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/38vuWiM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38vuWiM&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=cf164904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38vuWiM</a><br />\n<br />\n【註三】出口物料含石棉 香港上市中資遠大 貨櫃遭澳洲邊防扣查 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/38rUDAR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38rUDAR&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=aef3ec48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38rUDAR</a><br />\n<br />\n【註四】蘋果日報 : 一含鉛水辦來自內地預製廚房<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3avGlka\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3avGlka&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=89dd00ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3avGlka</a><br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n🌎 支持中港研究工作<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us-2%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=eff511cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us-2/</a>"},{"pid":"bb8e73cc7010b87ac11427fe404b5019a22cedfb","tid":1913791,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6d9fa7e400b9faaacce2494e981c6a1491d1fbf2","tid":1913791,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:34:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1df3c37f56ec7f93e18e8a1f6df9678eb2ca3323","tid":1913791,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"267ba7613972bf6ef214120d2a7277c9a3ec766d","tid":1913791,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6d63f222fa47b9bc22c4006275bd4e536e62bfac","tid":1913791,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"又係支那"}]}